{"tid":130501,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"平凡係好事定壞事?","createTime":"2017-02-22T12:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T05:08:50.000Z","uid":2863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"844624fc428e45bca8846071b58210001901aa62","tid":130501,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:35:10.000Z","msg":"恕我借呢度發言<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能有啲長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望唔好介意 <br />\n到底平凡係好事定壞事呢?<br />\n平時都冇咩朋友搵我，更唔好話女仔<br />\n之前既緣份計劃識既好快就傾傾下告終<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n興趣都係對男仔野多，運動就鍾意下籃球同單車<br />\n返左份新工無耐都冇乜同事想認識我/同我傾下計<br />\n除左坐我附近既媽媽級同事傾工作上既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算有望落大我幾年既男同事都係打個招呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以平時做野都係唔出聲自己做野<br />\n可能啲同事以為我唔多講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以唔多理我<br />\n反而一位90後女仔新黎左個幾星期(正常樣啦)<br />\n已經有男同事問佢有冇人陪食飯<br />\n其他媽媽級已經紛紛打探佢點解入左黎做，咩底細興趣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我都好健談好多野講架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自閉做野有時都好悶<br />\n佢地成Team人八成有玩『陰陽師』，小弟就冇乜點打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以冇話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係職場上人地唔熟悉你都係好事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n以免暴露自己太多野比人知<br />\n<br />\nSorry 1999咁，181長髮垃圾90後廢青字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f21f47ab8268bb00165d6d7338b3d26e215741b","tid":130501,"uid":3718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"好健談好多野講 <br />\n咁你有無係佢地面前表現出黎先<br />\n人地應該覺得你唔聲唔聲 好毒 單機果d<br />\n所以先唔理你姐？"},{"pid":"8d090ac9d73a5fd77c0ce27faece8be435add6fc","tid":130501,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好健談好多野講 <br />\n咁你有無係佢地面前表現出黎先<br />\n人地應該覺得你唔聲唔聲 好毒 單機果d<br />\n所以先唔理你姐？</blockquote><br />\n有時佢地傾開啲話題係我識既<br />\n或者佢地問啲野我知既，我都會答下爹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再講解下，不過完左之後都係繼續做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ed15ddeb5a27df7387e951d3d24421b5a963ed","tid":130501,"uid":2193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:48:03.000Z","msg":"我都成日諗依個問題<br />\n有時覺得係好事<br />\n有時又覺得好似好悶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e383764e3a3d5d170a21dba1be45d6898549e31","tid":130501,"uid":86634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"平凡是福啊施主 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">逃跑可恥但有用 啊結衣都係咁中意左星野源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"450b4f91c8a09502d7558aae4672469a04a1ccb7","tid":130501,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都成日諗依個問題<br />\n有時覺得係好事<br />\n有時又覺得好似好悶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得好事就係夠鐘Say個bye就走人<br />\n工作上只係比人話做得唔錯<br />\n又唔會有鑊要孭<br />\n壞處就真係有時真係好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想同其他人交流下吹下水<br />\n唔好好似我係外人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSOR好矛盾"},{"pid":"23f4da6c1392670a840ad2235275a9422d4f88c7","tid":130501,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平凡是福啊施主 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">逃跑可恥但有用 啊結衣都係咁中意左星野源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n上星期先睇完逃避雖可恥<br />\n其實係幾正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家係公司就好似星野源咁<br />\n唔多出聲做野，有問題先問一問同事點搞<br />\n自己搞得掂盡可能都唔想煩到人"},{"pid":"e870512c907c52ea4eeaaf8a3c8745d9bc0942a8","tid":130501,"uid":86634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平凡是福啊施主 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">逃跑可恥但有用 啊結衣都係咁中意左星野源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n上星期先睇完逃避雖可恥<br />\n其實係幾正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家係公司就好似星野源咁<br />\n唔多出聲做野，有問題先問一問同事點搞<br />\n自己搞得掂盡可能都唔想煩到人</blockquote><br />\n Ching係咪做IT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4ef9fd6b650253372b1d417aa55d3cc223080d","tid":130501,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平凡是福啊施主 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">逃跑可恥但有用 啊結衣都係咁中意左星野源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n上星期先睇完逃避雖可恥<br />\n其實係幾正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家係公司就好似星野源咁<br />\n唔多出聲做野，有問題先問一問同事點搞<br />\n自己搞得掂盡可能都唔想煩到人</blockquote><br />\n Ching係咪做IT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，係公司對文件多<br />\n有時再同外來人電話聯絡咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38359d729e6ddba1fd825eddb0fb2dad0b907591","tid":130501,"uid":10242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:29:08.000Z","msg":"唔一齊打機邊有話題"},{"pid":"e58fce5534feebb0db25181afa0c995bebc74943","tid":130501,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"平靜地單機放飯去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}